{"tid":49194,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句 唔支持港獨嘅人稱唔上香港人","createTime":"2016-12-21T14:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T06:08:54.000Z","uid":40847,"like":32,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a5b0879d280ac9686cc3340aeb44b79f1fbc0af","tid":49194,"uid":40847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:02:22.000Z","msg":"有好多反港獨嘅人覺得自己係中國人同時又係香港人<br />\n但其實呢啲人 根本稱唔上做香港人 只係純純正正嘅中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以唔好再口口聲聲話自己係香港人 乜撚嘢愛港 <br />\n係愛港嘅話就唔會俾佢繼續任由中國侵蝕 承認中國嘅統治 呢啲叫做愛國<br />\n咁唔該呢啲人死返上去大陸吸霧霾以示忠心<br />\n咪撚阻鳩住晒<br />\n真正嘅香港人係希望香港可以自己建設民主社會 捍衛自己嘅文化 <br />\n而唔係俾獨裁者控制住、做奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f6ec164c410f87b16216239dfed576f7a7696d","tid":49194,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:07:37.000Z","msg":"已閱，多謝"},{"pid":"ff689350b60b0252206e49688076139a43e130b3","tid":49194,"uid":13835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:08:35.000Z","msg":"咁唔係香港人但支持港獨又係咪香港人"},{"pid":"e0cfaec03e41367cee54aaeab2b653eb946f3e1f","tid":49194,"uid":13173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  班人成日諗住洗腦將中國文化同香港文化掛勾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老母臭閪 班中國人要宣揚中國文化就滾返上去啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"cbd13e7a2d14e3ed57a52dc649ca99610bc064cc","tid":49194,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:10:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"493534ff9b75308db52704fdec5f5de90607a759","tid":49194,"uid":16731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:12:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5d871236088df1aee2a09c2e5972ed9fb51d552","tid":49194,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:16:24.000Z","msg":"「得罪講句」嘅意義何在？"},{"pid":"76738fefb881781dc318b66869de4dea097d3edd","tid